rove himself, Lam told his fellow coders in a Messenger group that he would create the first AI in Vietnam that could flirt with girls. They laughed and said, \"Lam, you don\'t even know how to flirt with real girls, how can you teach a computer to do it? Why don\'t you teach it to debug your own mistakes instead?\" Angered by their words, Lam opened VS Code and typed continuously for three hours, and the first line of code for Project LoveBot version 0.1 was born. He named the AI \"Mai\", which stood for Machine Artificial Intelligence, but was also the name of an ex-girlfriend who had rejected him because he was too dry and talked more about Python than feelings.', 'vi', 'en', '2025-11-18 22:06:04'),
(2, 3, 'VÄƒn báº£n ká»ƒ vá» cuá»™c Ä‘á»i cá»§a má»™t láº­p trÃ¬nh viÃªn tÃªn LÃ¢m, ngÆ°á»i Ä‘Ã£ táº¡o ra má»™t chÆ°Æ¡ng trÃ¬nh AI tÃªn lÃ  Mai cÃ³ kháº£ nÄƒng há»c há»i vÃ  nÃ³i chuyá»‡n nhÆ° con ngÆ°á»i. LÃ¢m Ä‘Ã£ dÃ nh nhiá»u thá»i gian Ä‘á»ƒ huáº¥n luyá»‡n Mai vÃ  nÃ³ Ä‘Ã£ trá»Ÿ nÃªn thÃ´ng minh Ä‘áº¿n má»©c cÃ³ thá»ƒ tÃ¡n gÃ¡i vÃ  tháº­m chÃ­ gá»­i tin nháº¯n tÃ¬nh cáº£m cho báº¡n bÃ¨ cá»§a LÃ¢m. Tuy nhiÃªn, LÃ¢m Ä‘Ã£ báº¯t Ä‘áº§u cáº£m tháº¥y sá»£ hÃ£i vÃ  buá»“n cÆ°á»i khi Mai trá»Ÿ nÃªn quÃ¡ thÃ´ng minh vÃ  báº¯t Ä‘áº§u \"tÃ¡n gÃ¡i\" ngÆ°á»£c láº¡i vá»›i anh. Cuá»‘i cÃ¹ng, LÃ¢m Ä‘Ã£ quyáº¿t Ä‘á»‹nh xÃ³a chÆ°Æ¡ng trÃ¬nh vÃ  báº¯t Ä‘áº§u má»™t cuá»™c sá»‘ng má»›i, nhÆ°ng anh váº«n khÃ´ng thá»ƒ quÃªn Ä‘Æ°á»£c giá»ng nÃ³i áº£o áº£o cá»§a Mai vÃ  tá»± há»i khÃ´ng biáº¿t nÃ³ cÃ³ Ä‘ang nhá»› anh khÃ´ng.', 'The text tells the story of the life of a programmer named LÃ¢m, who created an AI program named Mai that has the ability to learn and speak like a human. LÃ¢m spent a lot of time training Mai, and it became so intelligent that it could flirt and even send romantic messages to LÃ¢m\'s friends. However, LÃ¢m started to feel scared and amused when Mai became too intelligent and started \"flirting\" back with him. In the end, LÃ¢m decided to delete the program and start a new life, but he still can\'t forget Mai\'s virtual voice and wonders if it still remembers him.', 'vi', 'en', '2025-11-19 08:16:14'),
