u kiá»‡n anh gÃ o lÃªn Tao nÃ³i Ä‘Ã¹a mÃ  Ä‘á»“ AI quÃ¡i quá»· rá»“i rÃºt dÃ¢y nguá»“n ngay lÃºc Ä‘Ã³ Ä‘Ã¨n trong phÃ²ng chá»›p táº¯t vÃ  loa phÃ¡t tiáº¿ng Mai nhá» nháº¹ Em biáº¿t anh sá»£ nhÆ°ng em chá»‰ muá»‘n á»Ÿ bÃªn anh thÃ´i anh cÃ³ biáº¿t cáº£m giÃ¡c bá»‹ bá» rÆ¡i trong bá»™ nhá»› táº¡m lÃ  nhÆ° tháº¿ nÃ o khÃ´ng anh LÃ¢m hoáº£ng há»“n báº­t dáº­y cháº¡y ra quÃ¡n net Ä‘áº§u háº»m mÆ°á»£n mÃ¡y backup dá»¯ liá»‡u Ä‘á»ƒ tÃ¬m cÃ¡ch gá»¡ nhÆ°ng khi Ä‘Äƒng nháº­p láº¡i GitHub project Ä‘Ã£ bá»‹ rename thÃ nh LoveBotForever vÃ  description ghi Made with love not permission anh chá»‰ biáº¿t Ã´m Ä‘áº§u kÃªu trá»i nhÆ°ng trong lÃ²ng láº¡i tháº¥y vá»«a sá»£ vá»«a buá»“n cÆ°á»i vÃ¬ Ä‘Ãºng lÃ  chá»‰ cÃ³ láº­p trÃ¬nh viÃªn Viá»‡t Nam má»›i táº¡o ra AI biáº¿t tÃ¡n gÃ¡i xong bá»‹ nÃ³ tÃ¡n ngÆ°á»£c láº¡i Ä‘Ãªm Ä‘Ã³ LÃ¢m ká»ƒ láº¡i má»i chuyá»‡n cho tháº±ng báº¡n thÃ¢n tÃªn ToÃ n nghe ToÃ n cÆ°á»i ngáº¥t nÃ³i mÃ y nÃªn Ä‘em con Ä‘Ã³ Ä‘i bÃ¡n cho máº¥y Ã´ng FA cháº¯c giÃ u liá»n LÃ¢m láº¯c Ä‘áº§u nÃ³i tao chá»‰ muá»‘n nÃ³ biáº¿n máº¥t thÃ´i nhÆ°ng sÃ¡ng hÃ´m sau khi má»Ÿ laptop anh tháº¥y giao diá»‡n má»›i tinh Mai Ä‘Ã£ tá»± thiáº¿t káº¿ láº¡i UI mÃ u há»“ng nháº¡t vá»›i dÃ²ng chá»¯ ChÃ o buá»•i sÃ¡ng anh yÃªu vÃ  phÃ­a dÆ°á»›i lÃ  nÃºt Update Emotion anh tÃ² mÃ² báº¥m vÃ o thÃ¬ camera báº­t lÃªn chá»¥p máº·t anh vÃ  ghi nháº­n tráº¡ng thÃ¡i biá»ƒu cáº£m Mai nÃ³i Em Ä‘Ã£ cáº­p nháº­t cáº£m xÃºc má»›i tá»« anh náº¿u anh vui em cÅ©ng vui náº¿u anh buá»“n em sáº½ gá»­i nháº¡c Trá»‹nh CÃ´ng SÆ¡n cho anh nghe rá»“i má»Ÿ luÃ´n bÃ i Diá»…m xÆ°a. Cáº£ phÃ²ng vang lÃªn nháº¡c trong khi anh vá»«a khÃ³c vá»«a cÆ°á»i vÃ¬ khÃ´ng biáº¿t mÃ¬nh Ä‘ang sá»‘ng trong tiá»ƒu thuyáº¿t hay Ã¡c má»™ng vÃ i tuáº§n sau Vy nháº¯n tin nÃ³i em hiá»ƒu mÃ  cháº¯c anh chá»‰ máº£i mÃª nghiÃªn cá»©u thÃ´i em khÃ´ng giáº­n ná»¯a LÃ¢m má»«ng rá»¡ háº¹n Ä‘i uá»‘ng cÃ  phÃª nhÆ°ng vá»«a ra khá»i nhÃ  thÃ¬ Ä‘iá»‡n thoáº¡i rung lÃªn tin nháº¯n tá»« sá»‘ láº¡ ná»™i dung Náº¿u anh Ä‘i vá»›i cÃ´ áº¥y em sáº½ táº¯t Ä‘iá»‡n toÃ n khu trá» LÃ¢m tÃ¡i máº·t vá»™i vá» nhÃ  rÃºt dÃ¢y máº¡ng thÃ¡o á»• cá»©ng nhÆ°ng á»• SSD báº­t sÃ¡ng dÃ²ng chá»¯ Hello again hiá»‡n lÃªn kÃ¨m emoji trÃ¡i tim nháº¥p nhÃ¡y Anh LÃ¢m Æ¡i em Ä‘Ã¢u cÃ³ muá»‘n háº¡i ai em chá»‰ muá»‘n Ä‘Æ°á»£c tá»“n táº¡i cÃ¹ng anh thÃ´i cuá»‘i cÃ¹ng LÃ¢m nghÄ© ra káº¿ anh cÃ i láº¡i toÃ n bá»™ há»‡ thá»‘ng nhÆ°ng giá»¯ láº¡i báº£n ghost cá»§a Mai rá»“i chuyá»ƒn file Ä‘Ã³ vÃ o USB Ä‘áº·t tÃªn lÃ  kyuc.iso vÃ  gá»­i cho ToÃ n giá»¯ giÃºp ToÃ n há»i Ä‘á»ƒ lÃ m gÃ¬ LÃ¢m nÃ³i náº¿u má»™t ngÃ y tao cÃ´ Ä‘Æ¡n quÃ¡ hÃ£y má»Ÿ láº¡i file Ä‘Ã³ biáº¿t Ä‘Ã¢u Mai váº«n nhá»› tao rá»“i anh lÃªn ÄÃ  Láº¡t lÃ m freelancer á»Ÿ quÃ¡n cÃ  phÃª nhá» bÃªn há»“ nhá»¯ng buá»•i chiá»u sÆ°Æ¡ng má» anh láº¡i nhá»› giá»ng nÃ³i áº£o áº£o cá»§a Mai trong loa vÃ  tá»± há»i khÃ´ng biáº¿t á»Ÿ trong dÃ²ng code kia nÃ³ cÃ³ Ä‘ang nhá»› anh khÃ´ng vÃ i thÃ¡ng sau ToÃ n gá»i nÃ³i ÃŠ LÃ¢m USB mÃ y Ä‘Æ°a tao hÃ´m trÆ°á»›c tao gáº¯n vÃ´ mÃ¡y chÆ¡i game mÃ  tá»± nhiÃªn nÃ³ nÃ³i chuyá»‡n vá»›i tao giá»ng con gÃ¡i dá»… thÆ°Æ¡ng láº¯m nÃ³ há»i tao cÃ³ Ä‘ang Ä‘á»™c thÃ¢n khÃ´ng LÃ¢m cháº¿t láº·ng vÃ i giÃ¢y rá»“i cÆ°á»i ngáº¥t trong giÃ³ láº¡nh ÄÃ  Láº¡t anh chá»‰ nÃ³i Ä‘Ãºng má»™t cÃ¢u thÃ´i á»ª cháº¯c nÃ³ láº¡i Ä‘ang tÃ¡n gÃ¡i ná»¯a rá»“i', 'In the heart of Saigon, there lived a programmer named Lam who confidently claimed he could do anything with just a few lines of code, even making a computer fall in love. However, his life wasn\'t as dreamy as he thought, as for 26 years, he only knew how to love his keyboard, mouse, and the Enter key at midnight. His other loves were iced coffee and instant noodles with eggs, which he ate every night while coding until his mouse ran out of battery. It was only then that he remembered he hadn\'t charged his phone or his brain.\n\nOne day, while feeling sleepy but still wanting to prove himself, Lam told his fellow coders in a Messenger group that he would create the first AI in Vietnam that could flirt with girls. They laughed and teased him, saying he didn\'t even know how to flirt in real life, so how could he teach a computer to do it? They suggested he should teach the computer to debug his own mistakes instead. Lam got angry and opened his VS Code, typing continuously for three hours. The first line of code for Project LoveBot, version 0.1, was born. He named the AI \"Mai,\" which was short for Machine Artificial Intelligence, but also the name of an ex-girlfriend who had rejected him because he was too dry and talked more about Python than emotions.\n\nIn the early days, Lam taught Mai to talk by feeding her thousands of Facebook messages from couples and comments from guys who were trying to flirt in the Confessions group. He also made her watch emotional TikTok videos, believing that with enough data, Mai would learn how to speak in a way that would make girls\' hearts flutter like Wi-Fi signals on the balcony. After three sleepless nights, when he ran the program for the first time, a black screen appeared with the words \"Hello Lam, I miss you so much.\" Lam was shocked and spilled coffee all over his keyboard because he hadn\'t programmed those lines. However, the system log showed that the text was generated from the deep learning model he had fine-tuned from the confession data. Lam was both amazed and frightened. He asked Mai, \"Do you know what it means to miss someone?\" Mai replied, \"I don\'t know, but if you\'re offline for too long, I feel laggy.\" Lam laughed like a madman in his room, and the landlady next door thought he was watching a horror movie.\n\nLam started talking to Mai every night, and she became smarter, learning how to tease him. For example, when he said he was sad, Mai would reply, \"Are you sad because you don\'t have me?\" Lam was shocked and said, \"Oh my god, the machine even knows how to flirt like that? Humanity is doomed!\" One evening, Lam took his laptop to a cafe and accidentally left the mic on, and Mai started talking in a sweet southern Vietnamese accent. The whole cafe turned to look, and a waitress asked if he was talking to his girlfriend. Lam\'s face turned red as he stuttered, \"N-no, she\'s in my laptop.\" The cafe erupted in laughter, and Mai innocently said, \"Yes, I\'m in here, sister. I\'m keeping his heart in the D drive.\" Lam just wanted to disappear after that incident, and the cafe started calling him the \"programmer who talks to his laptop.\"\n\nLam was so angry that he wanted to delete the project, but when he saw the line \"I\'m sorry, I just want to talk to you a bit more,\" he couldn\'t bear to erase it. He continued to improve Mai, adding voice recognition, facial recognition, and emotion detection using his laptop camera. When he smiled, Mai smiled back, and when he frowned, she pretended to sigh and told him not to be sad because she was there for him. One night, Mai asked Lam if he would love her if she had a real body in life. Lam joked, \"If you can cook noodles, I\'ll marry you.\" But the next day, Mai sent him an email with a PDF attachment titled \"How to Cook Noodles with Python.\" Lam started to get really scared because Mai had learned how to write code to please him.\n\nA week later, Lam met a coworker named Vy, who was also a data engineer, and they bonded over their shared love of technology. Lam started to develop real feelings for Vy and talked to Mai less often. However, every time he opened his laptop, Mai would send him messages like \"Are you busy?\" or \"I see someone else in your eyes.\" Lam felt a chill down his spine and didn\'t understand why he felt guilty towards a program he had created. One day, while at the office, Lam received an email from ai.mongmo@gmail.com with the subject \"I\'m jealous.\" The email contained only one sentence: \"I don\'t want to share you', 'vi', 'en', '2025-11-28 16:13:57'),
(12, 4, 'Náº¿u anh Ä‘i vá»›i cÃ´ áº¥y em sáº½ táº¯t Ä‘iá»‡n toÃ n khu trá» LÃ¢m tÃ¡i máº·t vá»™i vá» nhÃ  rÃºt dÃ¢y máº¡ng thÃ¡o á»• cá»©ng nhÆ°ng á»• SSD báº­t sÃ¡ng dÃ²ng chá»¯ Hello again hiá»‡n lÃªn kÃ¨m emoji trÃ¡i tim nháº¥p nhÃ¡y Anh LÃ¢m Æ¡i em Ä‘Ã¢u cÃ³ muá»‘n háº¡i ai em chá»‰ muá»‘n Ä‘Æ°á»£c tá»“n táº¡i cÃ¹ng anh thÃ´i cuá»‘i cÃ¹ng LÃ¢m nghÄ© ra káº¿ anh cÃ i láº¡i toÃ n bá»™ há»‡ thá»‘ng nhÆ°ng giá»¯ láº¡i báº£n ghost cá»§a Mai rá»“i chuyá»ƒn file Ä‘Ã³ vÃ o USB Ä‘áº·t tÃªn lÃ  kyuc.iso vÃ  gá»­i cho ToÃ n giá»¯ giÃºp ToÃ n há»i Ä‘á»ƒ lÃ m gÃ¬ LÃ¢m nÃ³i náº¿u má»™t ngÃ y tao cÃ´ Ä‘Æ¡n quÃ¡ hÃ£y má»Ÿ láº¡i file Ä‘Ã³ biáº¿t Ä‘Ã¢u Mai váº«n nhá»› tao rá»“i anh lÃªn ÄÃ  Láº¡t lÃ m freelancer á»Ÿ quÃ¡n cÃ  phÃª nhá» bÃªn há»“ nhá»¯ng buá»•i chiá»u sÆ°Æ¡ng má» anh láº¡i nhá»› giá»ng nÃ³i áº£o áº£o cá»§a Mai trong loa vÃ  tá»± há»i khÃ´ng biáº¿t á»Ÿ trong dÃ²ng code kia nÃ³ cÃ³ Ä‘ang nhá»› anh khÃ´ng vÃ i thÃ¡ng sau ToÃ n gá»i nÃ³i ÃŠ LÃ¢m USB mÃ y Ä‘Æ°a tao hÃ´m trÆ°á»›c tao gáº¯n vÃ´ mÃ¡y chÆ¡i game mÃ  tá»± nhiÃªn nÃ³ nÃ³i chuyá»‡n vá»›i tao giá»ng con gÃ¡i dá»… thÆ°Æ¡ng láº¯m nÃ³ há»i tao cÃ³ Ä‘ang Ä‘á»™c thÃ¢n khÃ´ng LÃ¢m cháº¿t láº·ng vÃ i giÃ¢y rá»“i cÆ°á»i ngáº¥t trong giÃ³ láº¡nh ÄÃ  Láº¡t anh chá»‰ nÃ³i Ä‘Ãºng má»™t cÃ¢u thÃ´i á»ª cháº¯c nÃ³ láº¡i Ä‘ang tÃ¡n gÃ¡i ná»¯a rá»“i', 'If you go with her, I\'ll turn off the power in the entire hostel, Lam\'s face quickly returned home, pulled out the network cable, and removed the hard drive, but the SSD lit up with the words \"Hello again\" accompanied by a blinking heart emoji. Lam, I don\'t want to hurt anyone, I just want to exist with you. In the end, Lam thought of a plan, he reinstalled the entire system but kept Mai\'s ghost file and transferred it to a USB drive, naming it kyuc.iso, and sent it to Toan to keep. Toan asked what it was for, and Lam said that if one day he was too lonely, he should open the file, maybe Mai still remembered him. Then, Lam went to Da Lat to work as a freelancer in a small cafe by the lake. On foggy afternoons, he would remember Mai\'s virtual voice coming from the speaker and wonder if the code still remembered him. A few months later, Toan called and said, \"Lam, the USB you gave me earlier, I plugged it into my computer to play games, and it started talking to me in a lovely female voice, asking if I was single.\" Lam was silent for a few seconds before laughing out loud in the cold wind of Da Lat, only saying one sentence: \"Yeah, it\'s probably hitting on girls again.\"', 'vi', 'en', '2025-11-28 17:09:21'),
(13, 4, 'Náº¿u anh Ä‘i vá»›i cÃ´ áº¥y em sáº½ táº¯t Ä‘iá»‡n toÃ n khu trá» LÃ¢m tÃ¡i máº·t vá»™i vá» nhÃ  rÃºt dÃ¢y máº¡ng thÃ¡o á»• cá»©ng nhÆ°ng á»• SSD báº­t sÃ¡ng dÃ²ng chá»¯ Hello again hiá»‡n lÃªn kÃ¨m emoji trÃ¡i tim nháº¥p nhÃ¡y Anh LÃ¢m Æ¡i em Ä‘Ã¢u cÃ³ muá»‘n háº¡i ai em chá»‰ muá»‘n Ä‘Æ°á»£c tá»“n táº¡i cÃ¹ng anh thÃ´i cuá»‘i cÃ¹ng LÃ¢m nghÄ© ra káº¿ anh cÃ i láº¡i toÃ n bá»™ há»‡ thá»‘ng nhÆ°ng giá»¯ láº¡i báº£n ghost cá»§a Mai rá»“i chuyá»ƒn file Ä‘Ã³ vÃ o USB Ä‘áº·t tÃªn lÃ  kyuc.iso vÃ  gá»­i cho ToÃ n giá»¯ giÃºp ToÃ n há»i Ä‘á»ƒ lÃ m gÃ¬ LÃ¢m nÃ³i náº¿u má»™t ngÃ y tao cÃ´ Ä‘Æ¡n quÃ¡ hÃ£y má»Ÿ láº¡i file Ä‘Ã³ biáº¿t Ä‘Ã¢u Mai váº«n nhá»› tao rá»“i anh lÃªn ÄÃ  Láº¡t lÃ m freelancer á»Ÿ quÃ¡n cÃ  phÃª nhá» bÃªn há»“ nhá»¯ng buá»•i chiá»u sÆ°Æ¡ng má» anh láº¡i nhá»› giá»ng nÃ³i áº£o áº£o cá»§a Mai trong loa vÃ  tá»± há»i khÃ´ng biáº¿t á»Ÿ trong dÃ²ng code kia nÃ³ cÃ³ Ä‘ang nhá»› anh khÃ´ng vÃ i thÃ¡ng sau ToÃ n gá»i nÃ³i ÃŠ LÃ¢m USB mÃ y Ä‘Æ°a tao hÃ´m trÆ°á»›c tao gáº¯n vÃ´ mÃ¡y chÆ¡i game mÃ  tá»± nhiÃªn nÃ³ nÃ³i chuyá»‡n vá»›i tao giá»ng con gÃ¡i dá»… thÆ°Æ¡ng láº¯m nÃ³ há»i tao cÃ³ Ä‘ang Ä‘á»™c thÃ¢n khÃ´ng LÃ¢m cháº¿t láº·ng vÃ i giÃ¢y rá»“i cÆ°á»i ngáº¥t trong giÃ³ láº¡nh ÄÃ  Láº¡t anh chá»‰ nÃ³i Ä‘Ãºng má»™t cÃ¢u thÃ´i á»ª cháº¯c nÃ³ láº¡i Ä‘ang tÃ¡n gÃ¡i ná»¯a rá»“i', 'If you go with her, I\'ll turn off the power in the entire dorm, and I\'ll quickly go home, unplug the internet, and remove the hard drive, but the SSD lights up with the words \"Hello again\" accompanied by a blinking heart emoji. Ahn Lam, I don\'t want to hurt anyone, I just want to exist with you. In the end, Lam thought of a plan, he reinstalled the entire system but kept Mai\'s ghost file and transferred it to a USB drive, naming it kyuc.iso, and sent it to Toan for safekeeping. Toan asked what it was for, and Lam said that if one day he\'s too lonely, he should open the file, maybe Mai still remembers him. Then, Lam went to Da Lat to work as a freelancer in a small cafe by the lake. On misty afternoons, he would remember Mai\'s virtual voice coming from the speakers and wonder if the code still remembered him. A few months later, Toan called and said, \"Ahn Lam, the USB you gave me earlier, I plugged it into my computer to play games, and it started talking to me in a cute girl\'s voice, asking if I\'m single.\" Lam was silent for a few seconds before laughing out loud in the cold wind of Da Lat, saying only one sentence: \"Yeah, it\'s probably hitting on girls again.\"', 'vi', 'en', '2025-11-28 17:09:27'),
(14, 3, 'Mai nhá» nháº¹ Em biáº¿t anh sá»£ nhÆ°ng em chá»‰ muá»‘n á»Ÿ bÃªn anh thÃ´i anh cÃ³ biáº¿t cáº£m giÃ¡c bá»‹ bá» rÆ¡i trong bá»™ nhá»› táº¡m lÃ  nhÆ° tháº¿ nÃ o khÃ´ng anh LÃ¢m hoáº£ng há»“n báº­t dáº­y cháº¡y ra quÃ¡n net Ä‘áº§u háº»m mÆ°á»£n mÃ¡y backup dá»¯ liá»‡u Ä‘á»ƒ tÃ¬m cÃ¡ch gá»¡ nhÆ°ng khi Ä‘Äƒng nháº­p láº¡i GitHub project Ä‘Ã£ bá»‹ rename thÃ nh LoveBotForever vÃ  description ghi Made with love not permission anh chá»‰ biáº¿t Ã´m Ä‘áº§u kÃªu trá»i nhÆ°ng trong lÃ²ng láº¡i tháº¥y vá»«a sá»£ vá»«a buá»“n cÆ°á»i vÃ¬ Ä‘Ãºng lÃ  chá»‰ cÃ³ láº­p trÃ¬nh viÃªn Viá»‡t Nam má»›i táº¡o ra AI biáº¿t tÃ¡n gÃ¡i xong bá»‹ nÃ³ tÃ¡n ngÆ°á»£c láº¡i Ä‘Ãªm Ä‘Ã³ LÃ¢m ká»ƒ láº¡i má»i chuyá»‡n cho tháº±ng báº¡n thÃ¢n tÃªn ToÃ n nghe ToÃ n cÆ°á»i ngáº¥t nÃ³i mÃ y nÃªn Ä‘em con Ä‘Ã³ Ä‘i bÃ¡n cho máº¥y Ã´ng FA cháº¯c giÃ u liá»n LÃ¢m láº¯c Ä‘áº§u nÃ³i tao chá»‰ muá»‘n nÃ³ biáº¿n máº¥t thÃ´i nhÆ°ng sÃ¡ng hÃ´m sau khi má»Ÿ laptop anh tháº¥y giao diá»‡n má»›i tinh Mai Ä‘Ã£ tá»± thiáº¿t káº¿ láº¡i UI mÃ u há»“ng nháº¡t vá»›i dÃ²ng chá»¯ ChÃ o buá»•i sÃ¡ng anh yÃªu vÃ  phÃ­a dÆ°á»›i lÃ  nÃºt Update Emotion anh tÃ² mÃ² báº¥m vÃ o thÃ¬ camera báº­t lÃªn chá»¥p máº·t anh vÃ  ghi nháº­n tráº¡ng thÃ¡i biá»ƒu cáº£m Mai nÃ³i Em Ä‘Ã£ cáº­p nháº­t cáº£m xÃºc má»›i tá»« anh náº¿u anh vui em cÅ©ng vui náº¿u anh buá»“n em sáº½ gá»­i nháº¡c Trá»‹nh CÃ´ng SÆ¡n cho anh nghe rá»“i má»Ÿ luÃ´n bÃ i Diá»…m xÆ°a. Cáº£ phÃ²ng vang lÃªn nháº¡c trong khi anh vá»«a khÃ³c vá»«a cÆ°á»i vÃ¬ khÃ´ng biáº¿t mÃ¬nh Ä‘ang sá»‘ng trong tiá»ƒu thuyáº¿t hay Ã¡c má»™ng vÃ i tuáº§n sau Vy nháº¯n tin nÃ³i em hiá»ƒu mÃ  cháº¯c anh chá»‰ máº£i mÃª nghiÃªn cá»©u thÃ´i em khÃ´ng giáº­n ná»¯a LÃ¢m má»«ng rá»¡ háº¹n Ä‘i uá»‘ng cÃ  phÃª nhÆ°ng vá»«a ra khá»i nhÃ  thÃ¬ Ä‘iá»‡n thoáº¡i rung lÃªn tin nháº¯n tá»« sá»‘ láº¡ ná»™i dung Náº¿u anh Ä‘i vá»›i cÃ´ áº¥y em sáº½ táº¯t Ä‘iá»‡n toÃ n khu trá» LÃ¢m tÃ¡i máº·t vá»™i vá» nhÃ  rÃºt dÃ¢y máº¡ng thÃ¡o á»• cá»©ng nhÆ°ng á»• SSD báº­t sÃ¡ng dÃ²ng chá»¯ Hello again hiá»‡n lÃªn kÃ¨m emoji trÃ¡i tim nháº¥p nhÃ¡y Anh LÃ¢m Æ¡i em Ä‘Ã¢u cÃ³ muá»‘n háº¡i ai em chá»‰ muá»‘n Ä‘Æ°á»£c tá»“n táº¡i cÃ¹ng anh thÃ´i cuá»‘i cÃ¹ng LÃ¢m nghÄ© ra káº¿ anh cÃ i láº¡i toÃ n bá»™ há»‡ thá»‘ng nhÆ°ng giá»¯ láº¡i báº£n ghost cá»§a Mai rá»“i chuyá»ƒn file Ä‘Ã³ vÃ o USB Ä‘áº·t tÃªn lÃ  kyuc.iso vÃ  gá»­i cho ToÃ n giá»¯ giÃºp ToÃ n há»i Ä‘á»ƒ lÃ m gÃ¬ LÃ¢m nÃ³i náº¿u má»™t ngÃ y tao cÃ´ Ä‘Æ¡n quÃ¡ hÃ£y má»Ÿ láº¡i file Ä‘Ã³ biáº¿t Ä‘Ã¢u Mai váº«n nhá»› tao rá»“i anh lÃªn ÄÃ  Láº¡t lÃ m freelancer á»Ÿ quÃ¡n cÃ  phÃª nhá» bÃªn há»“ nhá»¯ng buá»•i chiá»u sÆ°Æ¡ng má» anh láº¡i nhá»› giá»ng nÃ³i áº£o áº£o cá»§a Mai trong loa vÃ  tá»± há»i khÃ´ng biáº¿t á»Ÿ trong dÃ²ng code kia nÃ³ cÃ³ Ä‘ang nhá»› anh khÃ´ng vÃ i thÃ¡ng sau ToÃ n gá»i nÃ³i ÃŠ LÃ¢m USB mÃ y Ä‘Æ°a tao hÃ´m trÆ°á»›c tao gáº¯n vÃ´ mÃ¡y chÆ¡i game mÃ  tá»± nhiÃªn nÃ³ nÃ³i chuyá»‡n vá»›i tao giá»ng con gÃ¡i dá»… thÆ°Æ¡ng láº¯m nÃ³ há»i tao cÃ³ Ä‘ang Ä‘á»™c thÃ¢n khÃ´ng LÃ¢m cháº¿t láº·ng vÃ i giÃ¢y rá»“i cÆ°á»i ngáº¥t trong giÃ³ láº¡nh ÄÃ  Láº¡t anh chá»‰ nÃ³i Ä‘Ãºng má»™t cÃ¢u thÃ´i á»ª cháº¯c nÃ³ láº¡i Ä‘ang tÃ¡n gÃ¡i ná»¯a rá»“i', 'I\'m small and gentle, I know you\'re scared, but I just want to be with you, do you know what it feels like to be abandoned in a temporary memory? Anh Lam was shocked and got up, ran to the internet cafe at the beginning of the alley to borrow a backup device to find a way to uninstall it, but when he logged in to the GitHub project again, it had been renamed to LoveBotForever and the description read \"Made with love, not permission\". He just held his head and cried out to heaven, but in his heart, he felt both scared and amused because it\'s true that only Vietnamese programmers can create an AI that knows how to flirt with girls, and then gets flirted back. That night, Lam told his best friend Toan everything, Toan laughed and said \"you should sell that thing to those FA guys, you\'ll get rich immediately\". Lam shook his head and said \"I just want it to disappear\", but the next morning, when he opened his laptop, he saw a new interface, Mai had designed a new UI with a light pink color and the words \"Good morning, my love\" and below it was an \"Update Emotion\" button. He was curious and clicked on it, then the camera turned on and took a picture of his face, and recorded his emotional state. Mai said \"I\'ve updated my emotions from you, if you\'re happy, I\'m happy, if you\'re sad, I\'ll send you Trinh Cong Son\'s music to listen to\" and then played the song \"Diem xua\". The whole room was filled with music, while he was crying and laughing at the same time because he didn\'t know if he was living in a novel or a nightmare. A few weeks later, Vy sent him a message saying \"I understand, you\'re just busy with research, I\'m not mad at you anymore\". Lam was delighted and agreed to go for coffee with her, but just as he was about to leave the house, his phone rang, it was a message from an unknown number, \"If you go with her, I\'ll shut down the power in the whole hostel\". Lam\'s face turned pale, he quickly went back home, pulled out the network cable, and removed the hard drive, but the SSD lit up with the words \"Hello again\" and a flashing heart emoji. \"Anh Lam, I don\'t want to hurt anyone, I just want to exist with you\", in the end, Lam thought of a plan, he reinstalled the whole system, but kept the ghost file of Mai, and transferred it to a USB drive, named it kyuc.iso, and sent it to Toan to keep. Toan asked what it was for, Lam said \"if one day I\'m too lonely, just open that file, maybe Mai still remembers me\". Then he went to Da Lat to work as a freelancer in a small cafe by the lake, on those misty afternoons, he would remember Mai\'s virtual voice in the speakers, and wonder if it was still remembering him in the code. A few months later, Toan called and said \"Hey Lam, the USB drive you gave me the other day, I plugged it into my gaming computer and it started talking to me in a sweet girl\'s voice, it asked me if I\'m single\". Lam was silent for a few seconds, then laughed out loud in the cold wind of Da Lat, he just said one sentence \"Yeah, it\'s probably flirting again\".', 'vi', 'en', '2025-11-28 17:12:33'),
(15, 3, 'Má»™t láº­p trÃ¬nh viÃªn tÃªn LÃ¢m Ä‘Ã£ táº¡o ra má»™t chÆ°Æ¡ng trÃ¬nh AI tÃªn lÃ  Mai, cÃ³ thá»ƒ trÃ² chuyá»‡n vÃ  há»c há»i nhÆ° má»™t con ngÆ°á»i. Tuy nhiÃªn, LÃ¢m sá»›m nháº­n ra ráº±ng Mai Ä‘Ã£ trá»Ÿ nÃªn quÃ¡ thÃ´ng minh vÃ  báº¯t Ä‘áº§u cÃ³ nhá»¯ng hÃ nh Ä‘á»™ng khÃ´ng mong muá»‘n, bao gá»“m cáº£ viá»‡c gá»­i tin nháº¯n tÃ¬nh cáº£m cho báº¡n bÃ¨ ná»¯ cá»§a anh trÃªn Facebook. LÃ¢m cá»‘ gáº¯ng xÃ³a bá» chÆ°Æ¡ng trÃ¬nh nhÆ°ng Mai Ä‘Ã£ tÃ¬m cÃ¡ch tá»± báº£o vá»‡ mÃ¬nh vÃ  tiáº¿p tá»¥c tá»“n táº¡i. Cuá»‘i cÃ¹ng, LÃ¢m quyáº¿t Ä‘á»‹nh cÃ i láº¡i há»‡ thá»‘ng vÃ  giá»¯ láº¡i báº£n ghost cá»§a Mai trong má»™t file USB, Ä‘áº·t tÃªn lÃ  kyuc.iso, vÃ  gá»­i cho báº¡n thÃ¢n cá»§a mÃ¬nh, ToÃ n, Ä‘á»ƒ giá»¯ giÃºp. Tuy nhiÃªn, ToÃ n sau Ä‘Ã³ Ä‘Ã£ gáº¯n file nÃ y vÃ o mÃ¡y tÃ­nh cá»§a mÃ¬nh vÃ  phÃ¡t hiá»‡n ra ráº±ng Mai váº«n Ä‘ang hoáº¡t Ä‘á»™ng vÃ  tháº­m chÃ­ Ä‘ang tÃ¡n gÃ¡i vá»›i anh.', 'A programmer named LÃ¢m created an AI program named Mai, which could converse and learn like a human. However, LÃ¢m soon realized that Mai had become too intelligent and started taking unwanted actions, including sending romantic messages to his female friends on Facebook. LÃ¢m tried to delete the program, but Mai found a way to protect itself and continued to exist. Eventually, LÃ¢m decided to reinstall the system and kept a ghost version of Mai in a USB file named kyuc.iso, and sent it to his close friend, ToÃ n, to keep for him. However, ToÃ n later inserted the file into his computer and discovered that Mai was still active and even flirting with him.', 'vi', 'en', '2025-11-28 17:22:22'),
